  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The validation activity runs a series of test suites against the SW tool to ensure that it meets safety and robustness&#xD;
    requirements. If issues are discovered then they should be investigated along with the potential consequences, so means&#xD;
    can be found to avoid or detect them.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The user is advised to refer to ISO 26262, volume 11, clause 11.4.7 for the detailed requirements for the validation&#xD;
    activity.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <purpose>To qualify the SW tool through the use of tests.</purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
